"{\"uid\": \"irishcentral.com-news-mona-mcsharry-ireland-olympic-medal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Irish swimmer Mona McSharry has wonIreland's first medalof the 2024 Olympic Games in Paris, claiming Bronze in the 100m breaststroke final on Monday night, July 29.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"score\": 0.623420146978011, \"rank\": 0.5852236655325935, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\"}, {\"begin\": 85, \"end\": 90, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999775882318, \"rank\": 2.2411795659075092e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Sligo native overcame a slow start to finish with a time of 1.05.59, just behind Gold medal winner Tatjana Smith of South Africa (1.05.28) and Silver medal winner Tang Qianting of China ( 1.05.54).\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.6527908561589918, \"rank\": 0.48430622379636185, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999574825718257, \"rank\": 3.712919258667918e-05, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tang Qianting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry exploded into life at the 50-meter turn and surged into second place during the final 50 meters of Monday's final.\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tang, however, closed the gap to take Silver, while McSharry held off a stern challenge from Italy's Benedetta Pilato to remain on the podium.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.8673201271344395, \"rank\": 0.15297671847428448, \"text\": \"Tang\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\"}, {\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9223878894983398, \"rank\": 0.05976796080784478, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benedetta_Pilato\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Benedetta Pilato\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benedetta_Pilato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benedetta_Pilato\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry's bronze meal represents Ireland's first Olympic swimming medal since 1996 when Michelle Smith won three Gold medals in Atlanta.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9965217853345415, \"rank\": 0.0020672110211402807, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Fowler\", \"score\": 0.6520466811229543, \"rank\": 0.34220312778020484, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Fowler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Fowler\"}, {\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999971675653437, \"rank\": 2.831404691343426e-06, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Irish medal winner is also set to compete in the 200m Breaststroke, whose heats begin on July 31.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"score\": 0.623420146978011, \"rank\": 0.5852236655325935, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not crying, you are crying ?\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mona Mc Sharry, a bronze medalist at the Paris 2024 Olympics ?#TeamIreland|#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/y3WcMbyCi3    Sign up to IrishCentral's newsletter to stay up-to-date with everything Irish!\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\", \"score\": 0.999999992402536, \"rank\": 7.597405463074279e-09, \"text\": \"Mona\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry told RT\\u00c9 Sport on Monday that becoming an Olympic medallist feels \\\"unbelievable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999789533833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think there was a moment on the podium where I just started tearing up.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's when it was like, oh s--t, this is really happening,\\\" an emotional McSharry said.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's unbelievable.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a lot of hard work and I think there is always been a little bit of doubt - do I really belong at the top?\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This proves it.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I raced my heart out and to be on the right side of a really tight race is really unbelievable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry admitted it wasn't a \\\"perfect\\\" race and that her goggles filled up with water.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"Regardless of the result, even being able to compete at this level and confidently be in with a chance of medalling and then actually medalling - it's just what sport is about - those really tight races and just having fun.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes it's hard because you are so nervous to really have fun but that's the most important part, just soaking up these moments.\\\"\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry won her Bronze Olympic medal after considering leaving the sport a few years ago.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think almost walking away from the sport really put into perspective why I do it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These are just bonuses, and they are amazing bonuses, but it's all the friends, and the family, and the community that I meet and make along the way and that I get to share these moments with are the most important and that's just unbelievable.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then getting to be a part of tight races and putting yourself in those positions where you are digging deep and pushing really hard is just really fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry added: \\\"I was a little girl from a tiny, little village - and I still am that little girl from Sligo - and I was able to win a medal at the Olympics so it just shows that you can do anything you put your mind to.\\\"\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2787, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.6527908561589918, \"rank\": 0.48430622379636185, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am still that little girl from Sligo\\\" ?\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2941, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.6527908561589918, \"rank\": 0.48430622379636185, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tears are in full flow as the reality of Olympic bronze sinks in for Mona McSharry#RTESport#Paris2024?Updateshttps://t.co/NhnQoPxaeE?Watchhttps://t.co/b2OI4OoWVJpic.twitter.com/bq90VJUOak    McSharry was soon met with a wave of well wishes back home in Ireland.\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 3216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3024, \"end\": 3037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\"}, {\"begin\": 3072, \"end\": 3076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"t.co\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"t.co\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 3208, \"end\": 3215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9965217853345415, \"rank\": 0.0020672110211402807, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"President of Ireland Michael D. Higgins extended his congratulations, as did Taoiseach Simon Harris who deemed McSharry's performance \\\"magic.\\\"\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3231, \"end\": 3238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9965217853345415, \"rank\": 0.0020672110211402807, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 3250, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Higgins\", \"score\": 0.9353858500558628, \"rank\": 0.06907752622190391, \"text\": \"Higgins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Higgins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Higgins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ireland is proud,\\\" the Taoiseach added.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3363, \"end\": 3370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9965217853345415, \"rank\": 0.0020672110211402807, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 3386, \"end\": 3395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taoiseach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.399045719159197e-26, \"text\": \"Taoiseach\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taoiseach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taoiseach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's was magic from Mona McSharry!\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3426, \"end\": 3439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unbelievable turn and technique at the halfway point and what a battle to the end to claim Team Ireland's first medal.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3533, \"end\": 3545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.4001672377694024e-12, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"?\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ireland is proud ?\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3564, \"end\": 3571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9965217853345415, \"rank\": 0.0020672110211402807, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"?#Paris2024#TeamIreland@TeamIrelandpic.twitter.com/h5canue4Zk    Related:Sports,Inspiring\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": []}]}"